Dataset name: Actividades Culturales y de Ocio Municipal en los próximos 100 días
Dataset brief description: List of cultural and leisure activities that will be held in the next 100 days and/or are currently being held in Madrid municipal centers, with location, costs and descriptions by activity.
Maps of 14 plant functional traits (e.g., nitrogen, cellulose, chlorophyll) derived from AVIRIS-Classic airborne imagery over California between 2013 and 2018

Dataset name: U.S. Wind and Solar PV Supply Curves with Future Land-use Change
Dataset brief description: This dataset provides projected 2050 supply curves for U.S. wind and solar PV potential, accounting for land-use change under multiple IPCC scenarios, along with representative generation profiles.

A dataset containing information about duty pharmacies located in Madrid. The dataset provides monthly schedules and locations of pharmacies that remain open during off-hours, holidays, and emergency situations.
